<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_7765" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Frederick Beaumont an Alfred Escher, London, Mittwoch, 15. Mai 1872</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB03_001</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Tunnelbau</term><term>Gotthardbahn-Gesellschaft (GB)</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName key="Beaumont Frederick" type="addressee">Frederick Beaumont</persName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>London</placeName><date when="1872-05-15">15. Mai 1872</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Luzern</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B4611"/><ref type="next" target="B7735"/><ref type="next-in-corresp" target="B7767"/><ref type="previous-in-corresp" target="B3406"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p1"><lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <hi rend="printed">THE MACHINE TUNNELLING COMPANY, LIMITED</hi>
        </p>
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>
          <hi rend="printed">2. Westminster Chambers,
            <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>Victoria Street, <choice><abbr>S.W.</abbr><expan>SouthWest (Südwesten)</expan></choice> </hi>
        </p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>
          <hi rend="printed">
            <placeName key="London (UK)">London</placeName>
          </hi>
          <date when="1872-05-15">15<hi rend="sup">th</hi> May <hi rend="printed">187</hi>2</date>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7765_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>
          <choice><abbr>Mons<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr><expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan></choice> A. Escher<lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>– <add><choice><abbr>etc.</abbr><expan>et cetera (und anderes)</expan></choice> </add> – <add><choice><abbr>etc.</abbr><expan>et cetera (und anderes)</expan></choice> </add> –</p>
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7765_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>
          <placeName key="Luzern (Stadt)">Lucerne</placeName>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7765_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>Sir,</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7765_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>With reference to the advertisement
        <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>of the <date when="1872-04-05">5<hi rend="sup">th</hi> April</date>, calling for Tenders to
        <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>Execute the <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">St. Gothard</placeName> Tunnel. –</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7765_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>The Machine Tunnelling Company
        <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>hereby begs to confirm their offer
        <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>previously made. – <choice><abbr>viz<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr><expan>videlicet (nämlich)</expan></choice>: to Construct
        <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>the St. <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gothard</placeName> Tunnel at Ten
        <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>per Cent under the prices specified
        <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>in the estimate of the technical
        <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>report addressed to the Committee
        <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>of the <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">St. Gothard</placeName> by the Experts,
        <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/><choice><abbr>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr><expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan></choice> <persName key="Beckh August von">A. Becker</persName> of <placeName key="Stuttgart (D)">Stuttgard</placeName>, and
        <pb n="2"/><lb xml:id="p2-l1"/><choice><abbr>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr><expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan></choice> <persName key="Gerwig Robert">R. Gerwig</persName> of <placeName key="Karlsruhe (D)">Carlshrue</placeName><note type="transcript">sic!</note>, and to
        <lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>deliver the Tunnel complete after the
        <lb xml:id="p2-l3"/>lapse of 6. years from the date of
        <lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>our fairly commencing work. –
        </p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7765_p9"><lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>We will also find any
        <lb xml:id="p2-l6"/>reasonable guarantee for the
        <lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>fulfilment of our engagement
        <lb xml:id="p2-l8"/>that may be requested. –</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer"><p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p10"><lb xml:id="p2-l9"/>I have the honour
        <lb xml:id="p2-l10"/>to be, Sir,
        <lb xml:id="p2-l11"/>Your <choice><abbr>obed<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr><expan>obedient (ergeben)</expan></choice> Servant</p> </div>
     <div type="signature"> <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7765_p11"><lb xml:id="p2-l12"/>Fred Beaumont.
        <lb xml:id="p2-l13"/>Chairman of the
        <lb xml:id="p2-l14"/>Machine Tunnelling Company
        <lb xml:id="p2-l15"/>Limited</p> </div>
    </back></text></TEI>